title: ETERNALS TRAILER REACTION! Celestials & Thanos Timeline Explained!
author: New Rockstars
description:
Eternals Trailer Live Reaction! Who are the Celestials? Go to http://StoryBlocks.com/NewRockstars now to check out their plans and get one for yourself!

A new trailer for Marvel's ETERNALS (coming this November) has dropped, revealing the real reason the Eternals never helped the Avengers fight Thanos, and the Celestials' plan for Earth after Avengers Endgame. Erik Voss reacts to this trailer and shares his initial thoughts! Frame-by-frame breakdown of the trailer and its Easter Eggs coming in a separate video!
